{
  "id": "install-tutorial-datasources",
  "title": "Install Tutorial Datasources",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "## Installing tutorial datasources\n\nThis tutorial will make use of Grafana Cloud's test datasources. These datasources include Prometheus, Loki, Tempo, and Pyroscope that we host, containing custom data from real application scenarios.\n\nPlease follow the steps below to set up these datasources. Querying these datasources does not count towards your consumption of Grafana Cloud."
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-demodashboards-app']",
          "content": "Click: Demo Data Dashboards",
          "requirements": [
            "navmenu-open",
            "exists-reftarget"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='install-quickpizza']",
          "content": "Install the Quick Pizza SRE demo. This will deploy our tutorial datasources and trigger a page refresh.",
          "tooltip": "This will install the tutorial datasources",
          "requirements": [
            "exists-reftarget"
          ],
          "completeEarly": true
        }
      ],
      "id": "install-tutorial-datasources",
      "title": "Install tutorial datasources",
      "objectives": [
        "has-datasource:grafanacloud-play-prom"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "## Using the datasources\n\nThis section provides examples of how to select the tutorial datasources after installation in different areas of the product."
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/explore']",
          "content": "Click: Explore",
          "requirements": [
            "navmenu-open",
            "exists-reftarget"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "multistep",
          "content": "Select the datasource dropdown and choose the tutorial Prometheus datasource.",
          "steps": [
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Select a data source']",
              "tooltip": "Select the datasource picker"
            },
            {
              "action": "button",
              "reftarget": "grafanacloud-play-prom Prometheus",
              "tooltip": "Select the tutorial Prometheus datasource (grafanacloud-play-prom)"
            }
          ],
          "requirements": [
            "exists-reftarget"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid open metrics browser']",
          "content": "Click: Metrics browser",
          "requirements": [
            "exists-reftarget"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "id": "explore",
      "title": "Explore"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-k8s-app/home']",
          "content": "Click: Kubernetes",
          "requirements": [
            "exists-reftarget",
            "navmenu-open"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Select a data source-input']",
          "content": "We can form fill the tutorial datasource",
          "targetvalue": "grafanacloud-play-prom",
          "tooltip": "We can form fill the tutorial datasource",
          "requirements": [
            "exists-reftarget"
          ],
          "formHint": "We can form fill the tutorial datasource"
        }
      ],
      "id": "kubernetes",
      "title": "Kubernetes"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-app-observability-app/configuration']",
          "content": "Click: Configuration",
          "requirements": [
            "navmenu-open",
            "exists-reftarget"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "multistep",
          "content": "We can use a multistep to change each datasource in App monitoring",
          "steps": [
            {
              "action": "formfill",
              "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Select a data source-input']:nth-match(1)",
              "targetvalue": "grafanacloud-play-prom",
              "tooltip": "Select Prometheus first"
            },
            {
              "action": "formfill",
              "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Select a data source-input']:nth-match(2)",
              "targetvalue": "grafanacloud-play-logs",
              "tooltip": "Select Loki second"
            },
            {
              "action": "formfill",
              "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Select a data source-input']:nth-match(3)",
              "targetvalue": "grafanacloud-play-traces",
              "tooltip": "Select Tempo third"
            },
            {
              "action": "formfill",
              "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Select a data source-input']:nth-match(4)",
              "targetvalue": "grafanacloud-play-profiles",
              "tooltip": "Select Pyroscope last"
            }
          ],
          "requirements": [
            "exists-reftarget"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-app-observability-app']",
          "content": "Now we can navigate back to Applications to see the data.",
          "requirements": [
            "navmenu-open",
            "exists-reftarget"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "id": "app-monitoring",
      "title": "App Monitoring"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-metricsdrilldown-app/drilldown']",
          "content": "Metrics",
          "requirements": [
            "navmenu-open",
            "exists-reftarget"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Dashboard template variables Variable Value DropDown value link text grafanacloud-play-prom-input']",
          "content": "Here is how to select the datasource in Metrics Drilldown.",
          "targetvalue": "grafanacloud-play-prom"
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-lokiexplore-app/explore']",
          "content": "Logs"
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Dashboard template variables Variable Value DropDown value link text grafanacloud-play-logs-input']",
          "content": "Here is how to select the datasource in Logs Drilldown.",
          "targetvalue": "grafanacloud-play-logs"
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-exploretraces-app/']",
          "content": "Traces"
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Dashboard template variables Variable Value DropDown value link text grafanacloud-traces-input']",
          "content": "Here is how to select the datasource in Traces Drilldown.",
          "targetvalue": "grafanacloud-play-traces"
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-pyroscope-app/explore']",
          "content": "Profiles"
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "input[data-testid='data-testid Dashboard template variables Variable Value DropDown value link text grafanacloud-profiles-input']",
          "content": "Here is how to select the datasource in Profiles Drilldown.",
          "targetvalue": "grafanacloud-play-profiles"
        }
      ],
      "id": "drilldowns",
      "title": "Drilldowns"
    }
  ],
